To submit to Google Play Store, configure your eas.json with your service account key:

```json
{
  "submit": {
    "production": {
      "android": {
        "serviceAccountKeyPath": "./google-service-account.json",
        "track": "internal"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

For CI/CD, use environment variables or EAS Secrets instead of file paths:

```bash
export EXPO_ANDROID_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_KEY_BASE64="$(base64 -w0 google-service-account.json)"
```

Then submit your build:

```bash
eas build -p android --profile production --submit
```
